OL,5, The brother of a British-Israeli man   
OL,6, murdered by Hamas has told the BBC he  
OL,7, has never been more fearful of         
OL,8, antisemitism in the UK.                
OL,10,FBernard Cowan, from Scotland, was      
OL,11,Fkilled by Hamas gunmen in his home on a
OL,12,Fkibbutz in Southern Israel during the 7
OL,13,FOctober attack.                        
OL,15,FThe 57-year-old left his family in     
OL,16,FGlasgow when he was just 19 to move to 
OL,17,FIsrael.                                
OL,19,FHis brother Colin says he "is filled   
OL,20,Fwith dread" as a Jew living in Britain.
